@startuml
title 个性化偏好与设备别名参与执行顺序图
actor "家庭用户" as User
participant "DevicesView.vue" as DevicesView
participant "VoiceControlView.vue" as VoiceView
participant "PersonalizationCard.vue" as PersonalCard
participant "personalization.js" as PersonalAPI
participant "user router" as UserRouter
participant "CommandExecutor" as Exec
participant "personalization.py" as PersonalService
participant "ASRPostCorrector" as Corrector
participant "DialectNormalizer" as Normalizer
participant "CommandParser" as Parser
database "SQLite user_preferences" as Preferences
database "SQLite device_aliases" as Aliases
database "SQLite command_logs" as Logs

User -> PersonalCard: 保存默认方言或输入方式
PersonalCard -> PersonalAPI: PATCH /api/user/preferences
PersonalAPI -> UserRouter: preferred_dialect / preferred_input_mode
UserRouter -> Preferences: get_or_create then update
UserRouter --> PersonalAPI: updated preference
PersonalAPI --> PersonalCard: show saved

User -> DevicesView: 新建设备别名
DevicesView -> PersonalAPI: POST /api/user/device-aliases
PersonalAPI -> UserRouter: device_id + alias
UserRouter -> Aliases: check same user alias uniqueness
UserRouter -> Aliases: insert alias
UserRouter --> PersonalAPI: alias detail
PersonalAPI --> DevicesView: refresh aliases

User -> VoiceView: 执行“打开小灯”
VoiceView -> Exec: POST /api/commands/execute command
Exec -> PersonalService: get_or_create_preferences()
PersonalService -> Preferences: read preference
PersonalService --> Exec: preferred_dialect
Exec -> PersonalService: match_device_alias(command)
PersonalService -> Aliases: query current user aliases
PersonalService --> Exec: alias_match for target device
Exec -> Corrector: correct_asr_text(command, dynamic lexicon)
Corrector --> Exec: corrected text
Exec -> Normalizer: normalize(dialect from preference)
Normalizer --> Exec: normalization detail
Exec -> Parser: parse rewritten room+device command
Parser --> Exec: ParseResult with alias_match
Exec -> Logs: write preference_used and alias_match
Exec --> VoiceView: execution result
@enduml
